// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1160 — Mass File Rename (thegentlemen)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 4be535bd-2893-5080-a5bc-5fc7817697b1

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
